title: China United telecom and South Korean counterpart ink deal (Beijing Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Beijing Municipal Government ) China United Telecommunications Corp, the second largest telecom carrier in China , joined hands with its South Korean counterpart on Friday. The Beijing-based company inked a deal with SK Telecom Co
